=======================
Vim Environment Setup
=======================

git clone::

mkdir dotfiles
cd dotfiles
git clone https://github.com/fifth-sword/vim.git

install(zsh)::

sh dotfiles/vim/install.sh

NeoBundle Install(README)::

mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
git clone https://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim ~/.vim/bundle/neobundle.vim
Launch vim,  run :NeoBundleInstall

.. _NeoBundle: https://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim


